+<h2>Skanda Guru Kavasam</h2>
+<p><strong>Attributed author in the uploaded source:</strong> ஸ்ரீமத் சத்குரு சாந்தானந்த சுவாமிகள்</p>
+<div class="card">
+<strong>Publication boundary:</strong> This page contains only the manually checked opening invocation and lines 1–20 from the uploaded compilation. It is not presented as the complete work.
